org.springframework.messaging.simp.stomp

接口 ConnectionHandlingStompSession

  • 所有超级接口:
    StompSession, TcpConnectionHandler<byte[]>
    所有已知实现类:
    DefaultStompSession

    public interface ConnectionHandlingStompSession
extends StompSession, TcpConnectionHandler<byte[]>
    A StompSession that implements TcpConnectionHandler in order to send and receive messages.

    A ConnectionHandlingStompSession can be used with any TCP or WebSocket library that is adapted to the TcpConnectionHandler contract.

    从以下版本开始:
    4.2
    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev
